short_description: This US-SJ-60/FM 700 model differs from the others in that it has 2 winding parts, i.e. 2 heads. There are other models of this equipment in the description and their prices differ from each other.

This US-SJ-60/FM 700 model differs from the others in that it has 2 winding parts, i.e. 2 heads. The production capacity of the equipment is up to 55 kg per hour, the total power is 46 kW, the weight is 3500 kg and the size is 5.0 * 2.4 * 4.7 m. There are other models of this equipment in the description and their prices differ from each other.
